criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic renal anemia;

          -  Continuous stable intravenous maintenance epoetin therapy during previous month;

          -  Regular long-term hemodialysis therapy with the same mode of dialysis for previous 3
             months.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Transfusion of red blood cells during previous 2 months;

          -  Poorly controlled hypertension, that is, sitting blood pressure exceeding 170/100
             millimeter of mercury (mmHg) despite medication;

          -  Significant acute or chronic bleeding.
